title: Cambridge Texts in the History of Political Thought - 17 volumes
description:
A series of recent translations of classics in political thought, including Cicero, Augustine, Thomas Aquinas, Thomas Jefferson, Hegel, Nietzsche, etc.

Most volumes are in high-quality PDF format; a few are in CHM format.
